channel.topic:
Create your own interpretation of an Underground Hobbit Hole - simple words - Underground house. It doesn't have to be entirely underground. It can be in a stone hill or a mountain. Get your cobble and dirt generators going!

Underground Challenge - March 17th to March 30th

messages.content:
:grass_mound: Underground Challenge :diamond_pickaxe: 
We have seen a lot of cool colored overground stuff, its time to go underground. Create your own interpretation of an Underground Hobbit Hole - simple words - Underground house. It doesn't have to be entirely underground. It can be in a stone hill or a mountain. Get your cobble and dirt generators going!

:build_plate: Underground Challenge - March 17th to March 30th

📄 Guidelines:
:earth: Must be built in Minecraft Earth
:loading: This should be a brand new build and not be something that you've already built
:grass_block:  Build plate size will not matter & won't be a factor in judging
:mining: Feel free to ask for advice pertaining to your build in #underground-challenge 
:mob_of_me: All work must be done by one individual
:fast_parrot: Remember, this is for fun only
📌If it's a submission picture, please feel free to ask a moderator to pin it.
:sign: Winning submissions may be used in social media posts
